---
title: Hearty Chicken, Lentil & Cauliflower Pie with Cheesy Mash Top
description: There’s been lentils in a soup, lentils in a bowl, even lentils with rice and it’s all been so nice. Why not try lentils in a pie (that one rhymed too!)? Season them in aromatic chermoula flavours and stir through a tomato sauce with roasted veggies and chicken. Add a Cheddar mash topping to create the perfect pie for tonight’s dinner.
